OL,3,CDo you have what it takes to become an
OL,4,Con-call firefighter?
OL,6,FThere's never a "normal day" in our
OL,7,Foffice, but this one is definitely the
OL,8,Ffurthest away from anything I usually
OL,9,Fdo.
OL,11,FI was invited to Jersey Fire and
OL,12,FRescue Service to partake in their
OL,13,Fpractical taster session.
OL,15,FThe training sessions aim to give the
OL,16,Fpublic a sense of what training is
OL,17,Flike to become an on-call firefighter
OL,18,Fand encourage more people to apply.
