OL,3,CDo you have what it takes to become an
OL,4,Con-call firefighter?
OL,6,FCurrently, there is only one female on-
OL,7,Fcall firefighter on the island, and
OL,8,Fthe service is urging more women to
OL,9,Ftry out for part-time roles.
OL,11,FWhen I arrived, I was a bit concerned
OL,12,Fseeing the height of a ladder I was
OL,13,Fdue to climb, but that was the least
OL,14,Fof my worries.
OL,16,FThe session started with a cardio and
OL,17,Fstrength timed exercise. It involved a
OL,18,Flot of running and walking with heavy
OL,19,Fobjects.
