OL,3,CDo you have what it takes to become an
OL,4,Con-call firefighter?
OL,6,FAs you can imagine, it was hard work,
OL,7,Fbut achievable.
OL,9,FHowever, there was no time to rest, as
OL,10,FI was sent straight up that worryingly
OL,11,Fhigh ladder.
OL,13,FTo my surprise, this didn't scare me
OL,14,Fat all. I think I was concentrating so
OL,15,Fmuch on making it up there, I barely
OL,16,Fhad time to look around and see how
OL,17,Ffar off the ground I was.
