OL,3,CDo you have what it takes to become an
OL,4,Con-call firefighter?
OL,6,FOnce I'd made it up, the challenge was
OL,7,Fto hook my leg over the ladder, lean
OL,8,Fback, let go, and see what letter the
OL,9,Finstructor was holding on the ground.
OL,11,FDown I went and onto the final
OL,12,Fchallenge of the day.
OL,14,FI had to don a face mask and crawl and
OL,15,Fclimb through a series of corridors,
OL,16,Fmaking sure my left hand was touching
OL,17,Fthe wall at all times.
