OL,3,CDo you have what it takes to become an
OL,4,Con-call firefighter?
OL,6,FIn that moment, it made sense to me
OL,7,Fwhy people do this as either their
OL,8,Ffull-time or part-time job and the
OL,9,Fhard work they put in, to ensure we
OL,10,Fare as safe as possible.
OL,12,FTwo more welcome taster sessions will
OL,13,Ftake place at Jersey Fire & Rescue HQ
OL,14,Fon Saturday 16 November and Tuesday 26
OL,15,FNovember, with a female-only taster
OL,16,Fsession on Saturday 23 November
